Usage: setRouteBlkDefaultLayer [-help] {{[-layer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>] [-cutLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>] [-trimMetalLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>] [-drcRegionLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>]} | {-allMetalCut }}

-help                                      # Prints out the command usage
-allMetalCut                               # set 'fill' attribute
                                           # (bool, required)
-cutLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>       # specify cut layers
                                           # (list, optional)
-drcRegionLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>
                                           # specify region layers (list, optional)
-layer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>          # specify metal layers
                                           # (list, optional)
-trimMetalLayer <layerZ|{layerZ list}|all>
                                           # specify trim metal layers (list, optional)